Class AnalyticGeometryData

  • java.lang.Object
    • jp.ac.keio.bio.fun.xitosbml.geometry.AbstractData
      • jp.ac.keio.bio.fun.xitosbml.geometry.ImageGeometryData
        • jp.ac.keio.bio.fun.xitosbml.geometry.AnalyticGeometryData

  • public class AnalyticGeometryData
extends ImageGeometryData
    The class AnalyticGeometryData, which inherits ImageGeometryData and implements getSampledValues() and createImage() methods. This class contains following objects which are related to analytic geometry.
    • Geometry AnalyticGeometry
    • coordinates of boundary
    • coordinate of displacement
    • image size
    • delta
    This class is used in GeometryDatas, to visualize a model in 3D space. Date Created: Jun 26, 2015
    Author:
    Kaito Ii <ii@fun.bio.keio.ac.jp>, Akira Funahashi <funa@bio.keio.ac.jp>
